      "body_html": "<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Choose from 15 to 30 pieces. As you may imagine, the quality of frags will increase as quantity lowers. Please don't hesitate to let me know if you have any specific requests in color, structure, or species either. I am more than happy to†tailor the pack to your interests the very best I can.</span></p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><br></span></p>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">I will contact you after the order is placed to go over any specifics you may be interested</span></p>",
